1044
01:18:56,290 --> 01:18:57,562
Anything else?

1045
01:18:59,297 --> 01:19:00,338
No.

1046
01:19:01,439 --> 01:19:02,945
Any... questions?

1047
01:19:04,946 --> 01:19:06,028
No.

1048
01:19:07,822 --> 01:19:09,166
