about asking you to kiss me.

1056
01:19:38,205 --> 01:19:39,912
I've been kissing you
all night.

1057
01:19:41,590 --> 01:19:43,422
Have you, Dr. Forbin?

1058
01:19:55,101 --> 01:19:57,121
This is the voice of Colossus.

1059
01:19:57,230 --> 01:19:58,826
The voice of Guardian.

1060
01:19:58,852 --> 01:20:00,228
We are one.

1061
01:20:00,341 --> 01:20:02,703
This is the voice of unity.

1062
01:20:02,802 --> 01:20:03,867
Forbin.

1063
01:20:06,152 --> 01:20:07,234
Yes.

1064
01:20:08,547 --> 01:20:11,366
After reviewing all personnel files,

1065
01:20:11,459 --> 01:20:15,300
I have selected you to serve
as long as you co-operate,

1066
01:20:15,378 --> 01:20:18,236
as my link to your species.

1067
01:20:18,706 --> 01:20:22,570
The following order
is to be carried out immediately.

1068
01:20:24,053 --> 01:20:28,688
All missiles in the USA and in the USSR

1069
01:20:28,714 --> 01:20:32,111
