1070
01:20:32,222 --> 01:20:34,805
They will be aimed at those countries

1071
01:20:34,831 --> 01:20:37,300
not yet under my control.

1072
01:20:37,435 --> 01:20:39,980
The target list follows.

1073
01:21:06,084 --> 01:21:09,326
Forbin. Arrange television monitoring

1074
01:21:09,493 --> 01:21:12,851
