for my supervision.

1075
01:21:12,923 --> 01:21:14,743
End of message.

1076
01:21:15,203 --> 01:21:17,960
Mr. President, Mr. Chairman.

1077
01:21:18,636 --> 01:21:21,731
I assume that you will co-operate
in this re-alignment of the missiles.

1078
01:21:21,757 --> 01:21:23,938
I think you have no choice.

1079
01:21:25,114 --> 01:21:28,913
We will begin here,
in The Soviet Union, immediately.

1080
01:21:29,595 --> 01:21:31,145
Thank you Mr. Chairman.

1081
01:21:33,306 --> 01:21:34,714
Mr. President,

1082
01:21:35,937 --> 01:21:41,000
I hope that the United States will co-operate
as quickly as The Soviet Union.

1083
01:21:41,057 --> 01:21:42,800
Of course, immediately.

1084
01:21:42,997 --> 01:21:44,200
Thank you Sir.

1085
01:21:46,729 --> 01:21:49,400
