on their Complex 3-21.

1096
01:22:20,400 --> 01:22:21,622
Oh, Dr. Markham.

1097
01:22:21,651 --> 01:22:23,980
Just in time, Colonel Redham
was just filling us in.

1098
01:22:24,095 --> 01:22:25,683
You know everybody here
I believe.

1099
