Put that down here, please.

1113
01:23:15,272 --> 01:23:17,960
Remove the Warhead Arming Module.

1114
01:23:17,987 --> 01:23:18,995
Yes Sir.

1115
01:23:37,941 --> 01:23:40,935
The dummy module's in a false top
in that container.

1116
01:23:45,164 --> 01:23:46,565
That's the real module.

1117
01:23:52,760 --> 01:23:54,343
So far, so good.

1118
01:23:56,230 --> 01:23:58,861
Re-targeting.
Latitude nineteen degrees,

1119
01:23:58,887 --> 01:24:01,202
twenty-six minutes and five seconds.

1120
01:24:01,605 --> 01:24:03,789
Longitude ninety-nine degrees,

1121
01:24:03,815 --> 01:24:06,052
six minutes and forty-five seconds.

1122
01:24:13,073 --> 01:24:14,409
New adjustments.

1123
01:24:15,256 --> 01:24:16,518
Target set.

1124
01:24:26,103 --> 01:24:27,551
Here we go.

1125
01:24:28,986 --> 01:24:30,711
That's the dummy module.

1126
01:24:41,735 --> 01:24:42,664
Good boy!

1127
01:24:43,478 --> 01:24:45,159
Connect and wait for Colossus test.

1128
01:24:45,638 --> 01:24:47,079
Colossus testing.

1129
01:24:52,067 --> 01:24:53,257
Test completed.

1130
01:25:00,809 --> 01:25:02,250
Colossus satisfied.

1131
01:25:02,316 --> 01:25:04,256
- Yeah!
- We did it, it works.

1132
01:25:04,498 --> 01:25:05,639
We're going to win.

1133
01:25:06,467 --> 01:25:08,860
Just might beat the damn thing yet.

1134
01:25:09,204 --> 01:25:11,191
So you see, we feel we have
enough data compiled

1135
01:25:11,217 --> 01:25:13,131
to go ahead with the
overload program now.

1136
01:25:13,157 --> 01:25:15,061
And these are the latest computations?

1137
01:25:15,208 --> 01:25:16,600
The very latest.

1138
01:25:21,227 --> 01:25:23,600
Has Washington received conformation
from the Russians?

1139
01:25:23,696 --> 01:25:26,521
Yes they're standing by,
ready to overload their system.

1140
01:25:26,559 --> 01:25:30,355
At exactly 18:05 I'll call for our load
and run it through.

1141
01:25:30,599 --> 01:25:33,772
And two minutes after that,
we'll know if we've stopped Colossus.

1142
01:26:32,027 --> 01:26:33,370
Now run.

1143
