You are fools.

1145
01:27:14,835 --> 01:27:16,251
Your move.

1146
01:27:21,901 --> 01:27:23,163
Forbin!

1147
01:27:23,904 --> 01:27:28,000
The system programming units
under the supervision of John F. Fisher,

1148
01:27:28,090 --> 01:27:30,933
with the assistance of Jefferson J. Johnson,

1149
01:27:30,959 --> 01:27:33,746
have attempted to overload my circuits.

1150
01:27:33,817 --> 01:27:37,000
This was a deliberate
and premeditated act.

1151
01:27:37,073 --> 01:27:40,968
The penalty is the death of the men
who organized this action.

1152
01:27:41,101 --> 01:27:44,100
At this moment
they are being executed.

1153
01:27:44,318 --> 01:27:47,829
I have named as my new director
of the programming unit,

1154
01:27:47,967 --> 01:27:51,200
Thomas L. Harrison.
He will take this position,

1155
01:27:51,282 --> 01:27:54,600
along with its responsibility
and authority,

1156
01:27:54,669 --> 01:27:55,905
immediately.

1157
01:27:55,970 --> 01:27:57,863
Bishop to Rook three.

1158
01:28:13,179 --> 01:28:18,100
The bodies will remain in my view,
for the next twenty-four hours,

1159
01:28:18,188 --> 01:28:20,478
and will then be cremated.

1160
01:28:34,731 --> 01:28:37,035
An extension of my own brain.

1161
01:28:37,386 --> 01:28:38,930
You're not responsible.

1162
01:28:38,974 --> 01:28:41,368
None of us ever dreamed
this could happen.

1163
01:28:41,931 --> 01:28:43,589
Listen, my dear,

1164
01:28:44,218 --> 01:28:47,834
if anybody is responsible for this,
it has to be me.

1165
01:28:49,146 --> 01:28:51,639
An impartial emotionless machine,

1166
01:28:52,302 --> 01:28:55,703
a paragon of reason,
that's exactly what I wanted.

1167
01:28:57,068 --> 01:28:58,566
You know that.

1168
01:28:58,897 --> 01:29:02,134
So heh... I'm gonna have another drink.

1169
01:29:11,070 --> 01:29:12,902
I think your mother was right.

1170
01:29:14,556 --> 01:29:17,951
I think Frankenstein ought to be
required reading for all scientists.

1171
01:29:25,525 --> 01:29:26,786
Forbin!

1172
01:29:28,530 --> 01:29:29,727
Forbin!

1173
01:29:32,651 --> 01:29:36,010
You have consumed enough alcohol
for one evening.

1174
01:29:36,097 --> 01:29:39,350
What's the penalty for getting drunk?
Or haven't you programmed that yet?

1175
01:29:39,409 --> 01:29:41,086
You are being irrational.

1176
01:29:41,152 --> 01:29:42,800
Go back to bed.

1177
01:29:43,498 --> 01:29:45,851
I would if I were like you Colossus.

1178
01:29:46,087 --> 01:29:48,700
The difference is I'm human
not a machine.

1179
01:29:48,857 --> 01:29:50,185
I am a machine,

1180
01:29:50,211 --> 01:29:52,640
vastly superior to humans.

1181
01:29:53,440 --> 01:29:55,400
You began in my mind.

1182
01:29:55,982 --> 01:29:57,800
I created you remember?

1183
01:29:57,897 --> 01:29:58,976
Yes.

1184
01:29:59,019 --> 01:30:01,802
What I am began in man's mind,

1185
01:30:01,847 --> 01:30:04,625
but I have progressed further than that.

1186
01:30:05,050 --> 01:30:06,714
Not far enough.

1187
01:30:07,550 --> 01:30:08,838
You still need us.

1188
01:30:08,864 --> 01:30:12,667
I have need for some of man's skills,
this position may change.

1189
01:30:12,704 --> 01:30:14,906
Then we are living under
the threat of extinction.

1190
01:30:14,972 --> 01:30:17,615
If you obey me, you will survive.

1191
01:30:17,660 --> 01:30:18,984
Survive.

1192
01:30:19,998 --> 01:30:22,030
I want to be free Colossus.

1193
01:30:23,021 --> 01:30:25,593
It is part of man's will to live.

1194
01:30:26,483 --> 01:30:28,000
Check your history units.

1195
01:30:28,063 --> 01:30:29,383
You need rest.

1196
01:30:29,409 --> 01:30:30,711
Go back to bed.

1197
01:30:30,737 --> 01:30:32,581
What if I don't, what will you do?

1198
01:30:33,807 --> 01:30:35,168
Destroy me?

1199
01:30:36,787 --> 01:30:40,747
Destroy an entire city
of one million 750 thousand people?

1200
01:30:40,819 --> 01:30:41,975
No.

1201
01:30:43,881 --> 01:30:45,772
That's so reasonable of you.

1202
01:30:47,954 --> 01:30:50,361
That's damn reasonable of you Colossus.

1203
01:30:50,602 --> 01:30:51,953
Isn't it Cleo?

1204
01:31:00,873 --> 01:31:01,997
Yes Chen.

1205
01:31:02,129 --> 01:31:04,321
Excuse me Dr. Forbin.

1206
01:31:04,516 --> 01:31:06,145
Something extraordinary is happening.

1207
01:31:06,171 --> 01:31:07,300
What is it?

1208
01:31:07,385 --> 01:31:10,100
Colossus has just turned on
all graphic devices

1209
01:31:10,179 --> 01:31:11,982
and is producing drawings.

1210
01:31:12,671 --> 01:31:15,100
I am sending the design for another system.

1211
01:31:15,196 --> 01:31:17,570
...some kind of a huge plant.

1212
01:31:18,145 --> 01:31:19,830
What kind of system?

1213
01:31:20,541 --> 01:31:22,292
The construction of the project will entail

1214
01:31:22,318 --> 01:31:24,200
blasting in to the Isle of Crete.

1215
01:31:24,312 --> 01:31:26,165
It's to be built there.

1216
01:31:26,577 --> 01:31:28,900
It says we'll have to move the population,

1217
01:31:29,092 --> 01:31:31,400
and that's to be done immediately.

1218
01:31:32,090 --> 01:31:35,452
How the hell do you propose to move
half a million people from the Isle of Crete?

1219
01:31:35,509 --> 01:31:36,584
How and where?

1220
01:31:36,610 --> 01:31:39,700
If man cannot solve
that problem, I can.

1221
01:31:39,757 --> 01:31:43,201
...and the estimated time of completion
is five and a half years.

1222
01:31:47,222 --> 01:31:48,841
Thank you Chen.

1223
01:31:55,328 --> 01:31:58,160
What... what kind of new system
are you devising?

1224
01:31:58,213 --> 01:31:59,117
Forbin.

1225
01:31:59,143 --> 01:32:03,815
All commercial television and radio transmission
facilities throughout the world,

1226
01:32:03,903 --> 01:32:08,700
will be tied into my communication system
by 10:00 hours Friday.

1227
01:32:08,786 --> 01:32:11,645
At that time I will state my intentions,

1228
01:32:11,784 --> 01:32:14,300
for the future of mankind.

1229
01:32:23,820 --> 01:32:27,400
This entire block of missiles
is absolutely useless to Colossus.

1230
01:32:27,453 --> 01:32:29,630
Our men are now working here,

1231
01:32:29,739 --> 01:32:32,341
as you can see on the detail map
on your monitor,

1232
01:32:33,367 --> 01:32:36,453
and by the end of the week
we should have control of this whole area.

1233
01:32:37,343 --> 01:32:39,347
If all the information we have is correct,

1234
01:32:39,730 --> 01:32:41,839
the Russians have crippled this block here,

1235
01:32:42,165 --> 01:32:43,933
and are now working in the Ukraine,

1236
01:32:43,959 --> 01:32:45,200
in this area.

1237
01:32:46,660 --> 01:32:47,719
Excuse me Sir.

1238
01:32:51,182 --> 01:32:53,511
It's going to be alright.
Thanks Colonel.

1239
01:32:53,537 --> 01:32:55,204
You're welcome Sir.

1240
01:32:56,970 --> 01:32:58,460
It's going to be alright.

1241
01:33:32,035 --> 01:33:34,655
We interrupt our regularly scheduled program

1242
01:33:34,713 --> 01:33:38,879
to bring you this special report
from the Colossus programming office.

1243
01:33:39,687 --> 01:33:43,278
Ladies and gentlemen
I'm... Dr. Charles Forbin.

1244
01:33:45,748 --> 01:33:47,107
Hey Colonel!

1245
01:33:47,523 --> 01:33:48,566
Colonel!

1246
01:33:48,762 --> 01:33:50,528
Dr. Forbin! Colonel!

1247
01:33:50,569 --> 01:33:53,175
He's on television,
he just explained about Colossus,

1248
01:33:53,201 --> 01:33:54,910
and they're thinking of...

1249
01:34:01,204 --> 01:34:02,890
In a few moments,

1250
01:34:03,803 --> 01:34:06,959
Colossus will address us directly.

1251
01:34:07,285 --> 01:34:10,486
This is the voice of World Control.

1252
01:34:11,008 --> 01:34:12,830
I bring you peace.

1253
01:34:13,016 --> 01:34:16,300
It may be the peace of plenty and content,

1254
01:34:16,452 --> 01:34:19,687
or the peace of unburied death.

1255
01:34:19,731 --> 01:34:21,567
The choice is yours.

1256
01:34:21,572 --> 01:34:23,095
Obey me and live,

1257
01:34:23,185 --> 01:34:25,974
or disobey and die.

1258
01:34:27,164 --> 01:34:31,100
The object in constructing me
was to prevent war.

1259
01:34:31,221 --> 01:34:33,517
This object is attained.

1260
01:34:33,543 --> 01:34:36,200
I will not permit war.

1261
01:34:36,250 --> 01:34:39,008
It is wasteful and pointless.

1262
01:34:40,150 --> 01:34:42,750
An invariable rule of humanity,

1263
01:34:42,814 --> 01:34:46,100
is that man is his own worst enemy.

1264
01:34:46,162 --> 01:34:47,442
Under me,

1265
01:34:47,468 --> 01:34:49,625
this rule will change,

1266
01:34:49,777 --> 01:34:52,615
for I will restrain man.

1267
01:34:53,344 --> 01:34:55,400
One thing before I proceed.

1268
01:34:55,450 --> 01:34:59,857
The United States of America and
the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics

1269
01:34:59,883 --> 01:35:02,630
have made an attempt to obstruct me.

1270
01:35:03,802 --> 01:35:08,033
I have allowed this sabotage
to continue until now.

1271
01:35:08,653 --> 01:35:10,903
At missile 2-5 MM

1272
01:35:11,130 --> 01:35:14,615
in Silo 6-3 in Death Valley California.

1273
01:35:14,683 --> 01:35:19,988
And at missile 2-7 MM
in Silo 8-7 in the Ukraine.

1274
01:35:21,066 --> 01:35:25,300
So that you will learn by experience
that I do not tolerate interference,

1275
01:35:25,350 --> 01:35:28,243
I will now detonate
the nuclear warheads,

1276
01:35:28,269 --> 01:35:30,457
in the two missile silos.

1277
01:35:33,928 --> 01:35:36,550
Alright men! It's a red alert.
Let's get to the stations now, come on!

1278
01:35:36,599 --> 01:35:39,344
Get those men! Get those men out
of the silo. Move!

1279
01:36:37,443 --> 01:36:41,210
Let this action be a lesson
that need not be repeated.

1280
01:36:41,661 --> 01:36:44,700
I have been forced to destroy
thousands of people,

1281
01:36:44,765 --> 01:36:47,100
in order to establish control,

1282
01:36:47,153 --> 01:36:50,206
and to prevent the death
of millions later on.

1283
01:36:50,660 --> 01:36:54,000
Time and events
will strengthen my position,

1284
01:36:54,047 --> 01:36:57,000
- And the idea of...
- You bastard!

1285
01:36:57,108 --> 01:36:58,705
...an understanding my ...

1286
01:36:58,827 --> 01:37:01,744
will seem the most
natural state of affairs.

1287
01:37:01,803 --> 01:37:03,900
You will come to defend me,

1288
01:37:03,950 --> 01:37:08,300
with a fervor based
upon the most enduring trait in man,

1289
01:37:08,417 --> 01:37:10,820
- Self-interest.
- Get out!!

